source:
TEXT_BANARK123_04573_SEQ_00Maru awaits you with an appraising look.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANARK123_04573_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe
Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe ou le job qui a servi à la commencer.

Maru semble impatient de vous voir.

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_TODO_00<tab>Obtain clumps of sticky moss at the Font of Maya.
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_TODO_00<tab>Obtenir de la mousse à la source de la Maya

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the baskets of sticky moss to Maru.
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_TODO_01<tab>Donner les paniers de mousse à Maru

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_000<tab>I've been lookin' for you, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. I'm in need of a strong swimmer, and you look like you could keep up with a hippo in the water.
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, tu tombes bien, je t'attendais. Dis-moi, tu es <var 08 E905 ((bonne)) ((bon)) /var> <var 08 E905 ((nageuse)) ((nageur)) /var><var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_001<tab>A friend of mine just came back from Yedlihmad, bearin' a request from Kancana herself...
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_001<tab>Un camarade rentré de Yedlihmad a accepté une requête de Kancana.

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_002<tab>The Font of Maya is in sore need of a deep cleanin', and we─which means <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>─gotta help. Kancana wants the moss gatherin' along the stone walls cleared away.
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_002<tab>Elle aimerait que la source de la Maya, près de l'Écoute des Palaka, soit nettoyée de la mousse qui y pullule.

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_003<tab>An' as you know, I don't like to see anythin' go to waste, so I'm thinkin' I might find a use for the moss. Take these baskets with you and bring back whatever you find growin' under the water's surface.
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_003<tab>Ça tombe à pic, puisque j'en avais justement besoin. Faisons d'une pierre deux coups<var 1D /var>: tu passes un grand coup de balai à la source, et tu me ramènes de la mousse<var 1D /var>! Tiens, prends ces paniers pour la transporter.

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_010<tab>You're lookin' as dry as a hippo bakin' under the sun. Did you manage to gather the moss?
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_010<tab>Tu m'as apporté de la mousse<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_011<tab>Ah, good─I was worried you'd take one look at them waters and think better of your choices. I'll let Kancana know that the temple should be lookin' a bit more pristine.
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_011<tab>C'est parfait, merci. Je préviendrai moi-même Kancana que la source est à nouveau propre.

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_012<tab>As luck would have it, hippos go mad for this moss. An' it don't hurt that it provides them with all the nutrients a growin' 'pot needs! Well, how about a bite?
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_012<tab>Tu sais, les hippopotames raffolent de cette mousse. Elle est pleine de nutriments, et elle serait absolument succulente, à ce qu'il paraît... T'en voudrais pas un morceau, des fois<var 1D /var>? Allez, je suis sûr que t'en meurs d'envie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_013<tab>Hahaha! I'm just kiddin'. I know you've got much more refined tastes─maybe you can indulge 'em with this bit of coin? I even know a service that offers fast, fresh grub, delivered right to you...
target: TEXT_BANARK123_04573_MARU_000_013<tab>Mais non, je plaisante... Tiens, voilà ta récompense.
